\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 \hich\f0  \'93\loch\f0 I had spoken to Strongheart in my kind of la\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 \hich\f0 nguage, a language of thoughts and feelings incased in human sound symbols,\'94\loch\f0  Boone stated in}{
