\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 r\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 
ations. On this occasion I had slipped outside alone after a lively philosophical discussion in front of the fireplace. It was a hauntingly beautiful night, full of stars and magic, and I decided to meditate on my special piece of earth.
