The Strange World of Animals and Pets}{\lang0\langfe1042\langnp0\insrsid13595813 \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0  Vincent and Margaret Gaddis state that in 1940 Mrs. Ruth Whittlesey, the wife of a Protestant mini\hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0 
ster, was serving as superintendent of a convalescent hospital in Hawthorne, California.
