\par 
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af12\loch\f0  She would have me close my eyes and taking my hand would lead me to various places and I was to tell what surrounded us\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 trees, rocks, hills, grass\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 
